blender: blender (3D Content Creation Suite)
blender:
blender: Blender is an integrated suite of tools enabling the creation of a 
blender: broad range of 3D content with the singular benefits of cross-platform 
blender: interoperability. It can be used to create 3D visualizations, stills 
blender: as well as broadcast and cinema quality video. It features fully 
blender: integrated creation suite, offering a broad range of essential tools 
blender: for the creation of 3D content, including modeling, uv-mapping, 
blender: texturing, rigging, weighting, animation, particle and other simulation, 
blender: scripting, rendering, compositing, post-production, and game creation.
